{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1846030/extras/ezgif.com-gif-maker_116_.gif?t=1688393691\" /><br><br>Form your party and battle waves of enemies to level up, upgrade your warriors, and collect new, more powerful gear. Each time you enter a dungeon you'll be stronger than you were the last time, but don't let your guard down - the deeper you go the more ruthless the enemies you'll encounter, and every 100 floors a powerful boss will appear to end your run if you're unprepared.<br><br><strong>Note: HyperLeague Heroes is primarily an idle game but can be played actively as well.</strong><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1846030/extras/steam30.png?t=1688393691\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1846030/extras/banner_3.png?t=1688393691\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1846030/extras/ezgif.com-gif-maker_119_.gif?t=1688393691\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><i><strong>Infinite Dungeons</strong></i>: The deeper you go, the stronger the enemies (and the better the loot) you'll find.<br></li><li><i><strong>Active &amp; Idle Gameplay</strong></i>: Call the shots or sit back and let your team explore, slay monsters, and rack up tons of loot on their own. Play the game how you want.<br></li><li><i><strong>Dynamic Exploration</strong></i>: Treasure rooms, hidden boss encounters, and other randomized events make every outing unique.</li></ul><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1846030/extras/banner2_3.png?t=1688393691\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1846030/extras/ezgif.com-gif-maker_122_.gif?t=1688393691\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><i><strong>Create Your Own Hero or Villain</strong></i>: The power's in your hands, choose their stats and attributes and add skins from the Steam Workshop<br></li><li><i><strong>30+ Playable Characters</strong></i>: Enemies you encounter can be recruited to your team. Fill your ranks with valiant heroes, merciless villains, or bloodthirsty monsters, and upgrade them to create the ultimate unstoppable team.<br></li><li><i><strong>Character Fusion</strong></i>: Combine warriors to create powerful hybrids with unique stats and abilities.<br></li><li><i><strong>Take Your Team Online</strong></i>: Compete in challenges with players across the world to see whose squad can claim the top spot on the leaderboards.</li></ul><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1846030/extras/banner3_2.png?t=1688393691\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1846030/extras/ezgif.com-gif-maker_100_.gif?t=1688393691\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><i><strong>Procedurally-Generated Gear</strong></i>: All equipment you collect has unique stats and perks that are generated based on how far you've made it in your run, and since dungeons are endless, the variety of gear you can find is too.</li></ul><br>NOTE:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Features that briefly require an internet connection (once when starting the game) - login bonuses, shop, boost training<br></li><li>Features that require a consistent internet connection - cloud saves, leaderboards, achievements, Steam Workshop</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"First Steps","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1846030/0342ddf63381128c66b63470ca445f56f35defc6.jpg"},{"name":"Rookie Hero","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1846030/e1a77ebcab04bb8ee80349051b5967e1fc719ef8.jpg"},{"name":"Getting Good","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/p